            <summary>Seven sections of a larger Tantric treatise and manual on Śaiva ritual and worship containing seven different sections on different topics including Śiva pūja, Liṅga pūja, Pārthiva pūja (worship of an earthen liṅga), and worship of feminine forms of divinity such as Śakti and Dūrgā (in the form of Annapūrṇā).</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
